    <h1>Utila, Honduras</h1>

    <p>
        Utila is a beautiful island in Honduras known for its crystal clear water,
        tropical weather, and friendly people. It is a popular destination for
        diving and relaxing near the Caribbean Sea.
    </p>

    <p>
        One of the best things about Utila is the marine life. Many tourists visit
        the island to see coral reefs, colorful fish, and even whale sharks.
        It is a peaceful and amazing place to visit.
    </p>

